# Environment Variables Guide

## Server Configuration

```
PORT=3000                          # Server port
NODE_ENV=development               # development, staging, production
APP_NAME=Artisans Hub API          # Application name
APP_URL=http://localhost:3000      # Base URL
```

## Database Configuration

```
DB_HOST=localhost                  # PostgreSQL host
DB_PORT=5432                       # PostgreSQL port
DB_NAME=artisans_hub               # Database name
DB_USER=postgres                   # Database user
DB_PASSWORD=password               # Database password
DB_POOL_MIN=2                      # Connection pool minimum
DB_POOL_MAX=10                     # Connection pool maximum
```

## Authentication

```
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key         # JWT signing key
JWT_EXPIRE=7d                      # JWT expiry duration
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=refresh_key     # Refresh token secret
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRE=30d             # Refresh token expiry
```

## Mobile Money (Momo)

```
MOMO_API_KEY=momo_api_key          # Momo API key
MOMO_API_SECRET=momo_secret        # Momo API secret
MOMO_BASE_URL=https://api.momo...  # Momo API base URL
MOMO_PRIMARY_KEY=primary_key       # Momo primary subscription key
MOMO_SUBSCRIPTION_KEY=sub_key      # Momo subscription key
```

## Admin Configuration

```
ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@artisanshub.gh   # Admin email
ADMIN_PHONE=+233XXXXXXXXXX        # Admin phone
ADMIN_MOMO_NUMBER=+233XXXXXXXXXX  # Admin Momo number
```

## Frontend URLs

```
FRONTEND_MOBILE_URL=http://localhost:19000
FRONTEND_WEB_URL=http://localhost:3000
FRONTEND_ADMIN_URL=http://localhost:3001
```

## Commission & Fees

```
PLATFORM_COMMISSION=0.15           # 15% commission
MINIMUM_WITHDRAWAL=50              # Minimum withdrawal amount
MAXIMUM_WITHDRAWAL=5000            # Maximum withdrawal amount
```

## Email Configuration

```
EMAIL_SERVICE=gmail                # Email service provider
EMAIL_USER=your_email@gmail.com    # Email address
EMAIL_PASSWORD=app_password        # Email app password
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@artisanshub.gh  # From address
```

## Logging

```
LOG_LEVEL=info                     # Logging level (debug, info, warn, error)
LOG_FILE=logs/app.log              # Log file path
```

## Security

```
BCRYPT_ROUNDS=10                   # Bcrypt hash rounds
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=900000        # Rate limit window (15 minutes)
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=100        # Max requests per window
```

## File Upload

```
MAX_FILE_SIZE=5242880              # Max file size (5MB)
ALLOWED_IMAGE_TYPES=image/jpeg,image/png,image/gif
UPLOAD_DIR=./uploads               # Upload directory
```

## Optional Services

### Twilio (SMS)
```
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=account_sid
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=auth_token
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+1234567890
```

### Redis (Caching)
```
REDIS_HOST=localhost
REDIS_PORT=6379
REDIS_PASSWORD=
```

### AWS S3 (File Storage)
```
AWS_REGION=us-east-1
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your_key
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your_secret
AWS_S3_BUCKET=bucket_name
```

## Example .env File

```bash
# Server
PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=development
APP_NAME="Artisans Hub API"

# Database
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
DB_NAME=artisans_hub
DB_USER=postgres
DB_PASSWORD=your_password

# JWT
JWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_key_change_in_production
JWT_EXPIRE=7d

# Frontend
FRONTEND_MOBILE_URL=http://localhost:19000
FRONTEND_WEB_URL=http://localhost:3000
FRONTEND_ADMIN_URL=http://localhost:3001

# Commission
PLATFORM_COMMISSION=0.15

# Email
EMAIL_SERVICE=gmail
EMAIL_USER=your_email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your_app_password
```

## Setting Environment Variables

### Development
1. Copy `.env.example` to `.env`
2. Update values for your local setup
3. Source the file: `source .env`

### Production
1. Set environment variables on deployment platform
2. Use secrets management (AWS Secrets Manager, etc.)
3. Never commit `.env` to version control
4. Rotate secrets regularly

## Security Notes

⚠️ **Important:**
- Never commit `.env` files to Git
- Never share secret keys
- Use strong, unique values
- Rotate secrets regularly
- Use different secrets for each environment
- Store secrets in a secure vault (AWS Secrets Manager, HashiCorp Vault)

